casebody.data:
Nos. 614 and 615,

October Term, 1938.

Farmers’ Loan & Trust Co., Trustee, et al. v. Bowers, Executor. May 27, 1940.

Motion for leave to file a second petition for rehearing denied.

Mr. Justice Reed took no part in the consideration or decision of this application.

308 U. S. 634.
